Class ClearSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.impl.plugins.ClearSelection

  • public final class ClearSelection
extends NativeObjectContainer
    Datasets items selector plugin configuration element in order to have into the chart a clickable element to clear the selection.
